{"tid":786444,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"關公災難【林偉駿病逝】優品360°老闆：阿信屋10億樓下我有興趣","createTime":"2018-08-20T02:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T06:12:18.000Z","uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4c4cc6060e4391821530a5645135ebb78f243be1","tid":786444,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:30:57.000Z","msg":"嚫坤:我一向信奉『趁你病，要你命』這條金科玉律<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人地剛死,就想執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n對於759阿信屋創辦人突然離世，作為業務競爭對手的優品360&deg;老闆林子峰向本報表示擔心，因為怕759阿信屋會賣俾一個強者。他不諱言對759阿信屋（即CEC國際（759））有興趣，殼連公司市值約6億元，如果10億元以下都會有興趣，以免被強者崛起打倒自己。<br />\n<br />\n林子峰表示，佢（林偉駿）都唔識做生意，亂咁開舖，開成200幾間。舉例用3萬元租1間舖，租夠5間，先賺150萬元生意，租金佔收入10%。我都係租金佔收入10%，但我15萬元租1間舖做150萬元生意。另外人手及物流控制亦非理想做法。"},{"pid":"03c1416b5943f0c0ade0e07ebfac29f738060d64","tid":786444,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:32:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180820/58584596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180820%2F58584596&d=4T8dbDUuPIXk%2FVoA3xnEsZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=797a0731\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180820%2F58584596&h=23d46e55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180820/58584596</a>"},{"pid":"97bb620abc060d776dcb461a07a3ac6b3a04aec9","tid":786444,"uid":32765,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:33:46.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？"}